### Universal ###
# Common files that should be ignored in all projects

# Logs
*.log
# Temporary files
*.tmp
*~

*.bak
# Environment files (containing secrets, API keys, credentials)
.env
*.env
.env.*

# Local configuration that shouldn't be shared
*.local

